org.hibernate.jpa.spi

Class AbstractQueryImpl<X>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.jpa.spi.BaseQueryImpl
      • org.hibernate.jpa.spi.AbstractQueryImpl<X>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Query, TypedQuery<X>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractQueryImpl, QueryImpl

    public abstract class AbstractQueryImpl<X>
extends BaseQueryImpl
implements TypedQuery<X>
    Base class for implementing both Query and TypedQuery, including query references built from criteria queries.

    Not intended as base for StoredProcedureQuery
